{"id":320730,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/11/global-voices-秘鲁：管制垃圾食物等于限制自由？/","date":"2013-11-02T02:00:16Z","modified":"2013-11-02T02:00:16Z","title":"Global Voices | 秘鲁：管制垃圾食物等于限制自由？","content":"<p><p>秘鲁独特的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/fdc/welcome_mjx.shtml\">烹饪法</a>一直是国内外非常热门的话题，但近来引起大众热烈讨论的饮食议题，既不是料理品质的高低，也不是传统食材的新应用，而是秘鲁统总乌马拉（Ollanta Humala）所<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.larepublica.pe/16-05-2013/humala-creen-que-pueden-poner-cualquier-cosa-en-la-boca-de-los-ninos\">颁布</a>的法令，儿童及青少年推广健康饮食法（the Law of the Promotion of Healthy Eating by Boys, Girls, and Adolescents）。</p>\n<p>该<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://es.consumersinternational.org/media/1323665/ley%20sobre%20alimentaci%C3%B3n%20sana,%20per%C3%BA,%203013.pdf\">法令</a>颁布于2013年5月17日，此规定的目的为“透过教育，加强及促进体育性活动并在中小学设立提供健康食物的午餐商家，藉此有效促进及确保人民的公共卫生健康及儿童的正常成长及发育，也同时监督所有针对儿童及青少年设计的行销广告内容及活动。”</p>\n<p>国会在5月2日通过这项法案，议员路易士（Luis Galarreta）<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://luchogalarreta.pe/noticias/ley-contra-comida-chatarra-tiene-vision-intervencionista/\">宣称</a>这是一项“干涉商业行为的法条，将严重影响媒体及其财务状况”，同时前外贸旅游部长阿尔弗雷德．费雷罗（Minister of Foreign Trade and Tourism, Alfredo Ferrero）甚至说这样<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://gestion.pe/politica/alfredo-ferrero-ley-comida-chatarra-podria-afectar-transimison-mundial-brasil-2014-2066366\">意义不明的法案</a>将“影响2014年巴西世界杯的宣传（the Brazil World Cup in 2014）”。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://es.globalvoicesonline.org/author/juan-arellano/\" title=\"文章导读 Juan Arellano\">Juan Arellano</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://es.globalvoicesonline.org/2013/05/21/peru-la-comida-chatarra-es-sinonimo-de-libertad/\" title=\"阅读原文  es\">阅读原文  es</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/11/02/12946/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E7%A7%98%E9%B2%81%EF%BC%9A%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%9F&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F11%2F02%2F12946%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F11%2F02%2F12946%2F&#038;desc=%E7%A7%98%E9%B2%81%EF%BC%9A%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F11%2F02%2F12946%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F11%2F02%2F12946%2F&#038;text=%E7%A7%98%E9%B2%81%EF%BC%9A%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%9F&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F11%2F02%2F12946%2F\" title=\"googleplus\"><span>googleplus</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://reddit.co